Other amenities include a guest suite, 24-hour fitness center, 2 party rooms, solarium and lobby. Bower Hill III is located on the bus line and is in the award winning Mt. Lebanon school district. Less than 1 mile away from St. Clair Hospital, Bower Hill also has easy access to Rt. 19, I-376, I-79 and downtown Pittsburgh. Come visit us at Bower Hill III in Mt. Lebanon, PA 15234!

name: Lando Lofts
description:
All-Inclusive Lofts:
Imagine a private apartment just for your business guests. Ready whenever you need it, it’s a cost effective housing solution with amenities even a five star hotel can’t offer. Your clients will enjoy the best of Pittsburgh, from fine dining and theater to martini bars and sports.
Lando Lofts is that apartment. Located at 909 Penn Avenue, in the heart of Pittsburgh’s Cultural District, Lando Lofts is big city luxury that no guest will soon forget, and an excuse to make their trip to Pittsburgh a business visit and a vacation. You will enjoy:
•Quartz counter tops and slow close cabinets in bright kitchens
•Huge windows, open floor plans and plenty of natural light
•A beautiful rooftop deck equipped to serve dinner and drinks
Live the Lando Life. Walking, dining, socializing, taking in all of the city activity around you. Featuring gourmet kitchens with gas ranges and huge quartz-topped islands, Lando Lofts are the premier loft residences in Downtown Pittsburgh’s Cultural District. Seek inspirational living and impressive entertaining – this is your spot amidst all of the action. Lando Lofts roof top kitchen allows you to entertain outside and enjoy a dinner party on the roof. Otherwise you can stroll outside along the river trails a take a bike ride

name: The Cork Factory Lofts
description: On the water yet in the heart of Pittsburgh's historic Strip District, there's no place quite like The Cork Factory. Finally, an address that's as interesting as you are. Originally constructed in 1901 as the Armstrong Cork Factory, this landmark structure has been artfully converted into 297 Loft Apartments in the heart of Pittsburgh's popular Strip District. The nightlife, the shopping, the history, the recreation --it's yours for the taking. Wake up to a breathtaking view of the Pittsburgh skyline right outside your window. Make a latte run up the block or, better yet, brew it at home and sip it poolside or at river's edge. You can check the morning news online in the Courtyard Garden with our wireless internet access. Your day is just beginning and there's no telling where it will take you. We look forward to you making your new home at the address and location that will impress your friends, and the comfort and ease of living that will impress you!

name: The Venue
description: Welcome to The Venue Apartments. Our luxurious waterfront pet friendly apartments with arguably the best views in downtown Pittsburgh offer newly renovated one and two bedroom apartments with all new modern upgrades. Some of the best views in town include panoramic views of the Allegheny River, PNC Park, Heinz Field and the North Shore. Live Smart at The Venue Apartments in downtown Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania with the most modernized Bluetooth enabled features such as Free Wifi in common area, ride sharing Uber waiting lounge, Nest home security cameras and Bluetooth enabled front door locks all activated from your smart phone, plus smart lighting in all units and LCD display front door peep holes among many other Smart features. The location can't be beat either. One block away from the north shore connector T station, walking distance to Market Square, On/Off access to bike trails and canoeing, walking distance to the theatres, nightlife entertainment and dining. The pinnacle of Apartments in downtown Pittsburgh is waiting for you, unmatched in its amenity rich renovations and conveniences.

For over a century, Oakland and Shadyside have served as Pittsburgh's cultural hub. The University of Pittsburgh, Carlow College and Carnegie Mellon are known around the world. The University of Pittsburgh for its highly-acclaimed medical facilities, sports programs and research, and Carnegie Mellon for its technological breakthroughs are two of the finest universities in the country. These two universities have drawn together to form a prominent community with a very distinctive lifestyle. Devon Towers sits conveniently in the heart of this very versatile community which draws even more diversity from the business district of Shadyside, located just a few blocks away. Shadyside boasts some of the finest shopping in the city of Pittsburgh. With the diversity of the stores and eating establishments offered in this small, but quaint three block radius, Shadyside provides everyone the opportunity to obtain whatever their lifestyle demands. Inside Devon Towers offers excellence in every detail. Apartments are exceptionally spacious, offering a wide variety of distinctive features. For over a century, Oakland has served as Pittsburgh's cultural hub. The University of Pittsburgh, and its world renowned medical facilities, sports programs and research institutes have drawn together a prominent community with a very distinctive lifestyle. The Fairfax sits at the heart of this dynamic neighborhood. Within a three block radius can be found the Carnegie Museum of Art and Natural History, Carnegie Music Hall, Schenley Park and the Campus of Carnegie Mellon University. Equally as prominent are the many fine shops and restaurants and businesses which serve the vibrant community of Oakland. Public transportation is convenient to Pittsburgh. Inside, the Fairfax offers excellence in every detail. Apartments are exceptionally spacious, offering a wide variety of distinctive features, including crown molding and expansive closet space. Fully equipped kitchens, controlled heating and air conditioning, and intercom entry are standard features. The Fairfax also boasts a quiet landscaped courtyard, fully equipped exercise center, roof top deck, and 24 hour emergency maintenance. It is all Grand Elegance at a Grand Address. We Welcome You!

The apartments have been officially opened for rentals in August 2016 ! (Last Updated: 2016-11-21)
